1. *Oči* su joj sjajile od sreće. (Her *eyes* were shining with happiness.)
2. Videla sam *oči* u mraku. (I saw *eyes* in the dark.)
3. Sestre imaju plave *oči*. (The sisters have blue *eyes*.)
4. Dete je zatvorilo *oči* i zaspalo. (The child closed their *eyes* and fell asleep.)
5. *Oči* su joj bile uperene u mene. (Her *eyes* were fixed on me.)
6. Moram da posetim očnog lekara jer me bole *oči*. (I have to visit an eye doctor because my *eyes* hurt.)
7. Tata mi ima zelene *oči*. (My dad has green *eyes*.)
8. Ustaj, otvori *oči* i pogledaj kako je lep dan! (Get up, open your *eyes* and see how beautiful the day is!)
9. Pogledaj me u *oči* i reci mi istinu. (Look me in the *eyes* and tell me the truth.)
10. *Oči* su ogledalo duše. (The *eyes* are the mirror of the soul.)